summary: This is the first face preset that I made.
descriptionHtml:
[size=3]This is my first face preset and I thought it would be great to share it. She is a Nord race. [/size]

[color=#ffe599]
[size=4][b]Requirements:[/b][/size][/color]

[color=#6fa8dc][size=3][url=http://skse.silverlock.org/]SKSE[/url][/size][/color]
[size=3][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]RaceMenu[/url][/size]
[size=3][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?]The Eyes Of Beauty[/url]
[/size][size=3][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68311/?]KS Hairdos Renewal[/url]
[/size][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/7127/?][size=3]RANs HeadMesh Variants Type C

[/size][/url][size=3]If you want her to look like she does in the image I use [/size][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2666/?][size=3]CBBE[/size][/url][size=3] and [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/54362/?]Somber Dreams ENB[/url].

[/size][size=4][b][color=#ffe599]Install:[/color]

[/b][/size][size=3]You can install with NMM or manually download it, unzip it and place it in your Skyrim/Data/SKSE/P[b]lugins/[/b][b]CharGen/Presets
[/b]
In game, pull up the console command and type showracemenu and hit enter, pick Nord race, hit the the preset tab and load the presets by using F9 and pick Talia.[/size]

[color=#ffe599][size=4]Armor in images-[/size][/color][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/53697/?][size=3] [/size][size=3]Midnight Breed
